OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNHS staff sickness hits    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frecord high in England     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Staff sickness in the NHS in England   
OL,6, has reached record levels.             
OL,8,FFigures for 2022 show an absence rate -
OL,9,Fthe proportion of days lost - of 5.6%, 
OL,10,Fmeaning the NHS lost the equivalent of 
OL,11,Fnearly 75,000 staff to illness.        
OL,13,FThis is higher than during the peak    
OL,14,Fpandemic years of 2020 and 2021 - and a
OL,15,F29% rise on the 2019 rate.             
OL,17,FMental health problems were the most   
OL,18,Fcommon cause, responsible for nearly a 
OL,19,Fquarter of absences, the Nuffield Trust
OL,20,Fanalysis of official NHS data shows.   
